data.description: 1004 Wintu Ct. is the GEM of the Dakota Ridge Subdivision.  This 6 bed/ 4 bath home is nestled into a private cul-de-sac on .46 acres of lush landscape.  The home boasts vaulted 2 story entry, cathedral ceilings, hardwood floors, in-law arrangement, 1st floor laundry and more.  The spacious family room houses a multi-sided fireplace with living room to create the prefect setting for all your entertaining opportunities.  The custom kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, beautiful hardwood floors, L shaped island for everyone to gather around.  The oversized sliders will lead you into the rolling semi private back yard.  The primary bedroom serves as the perfect retreat after a long day.  Enjoy the fireplace, ensuite and balcony where you can sit outside and wish on a star.  Can't sleep?  No worries,  you can curl up with your favorite book and read in the attached library.  The finished basement is the perfect set up for an in-law arrangement or the best house on the block for slumber parties complete with bedroom 5/6 as well as a full bathroom. Home is equipped with new dual heat/dual air so you will never be too cold or too hot anywhere in this 4000 sq ft (Incl basesment) home! You don't want to miss this stunning home.  Call to schedule your appointment today.
